                                    size="3">An <i>updateMode</i> attribute to indicate whether the item should be "added",</font> or<font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">"altered" (mandatory). Death notification status cannot be removed using messaging.</font>
                                    </li>
                                    </ul>
                                    <p>This attribute should be used in the following way:</p>
                                    <ul>
