                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">
                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">This attribute shall be used in conjunction with the <em>updateMode</em> attribute of <em>Consent </em>in the following way:</font>
                                    <ul>
                                    <li>
                                    <font
                                    face="Times New Roman" size="3">If the <em>updateMode</em> is set to "removed", this attribute may only be set to "6" (Call centre call-back consent)</font>
                                    </li>
